      },
      "date": "2012-08-26 06:05:39.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Tests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/c41b362a-ee84-11e1-8e98-52540035b04c). Ran 3 tests. 1 tests failed: posix.\n\nThe LSB-VSX POSIX test suite was built and executed successfully. It found three failures: link.15, mkdir.12 and rename.35. All of them are related to LINK_MAX. Since Lustre allows a higher link count than glibc expects, I disabled those three sub-tests in myscen.exec, pushed the change to toolkit repo and re-triggerred the posix test. Let's wait for the new result...",
